edu.ucdavis.cstars.client.layers

Class WMTSLayer.ResourceInfo

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.google.gwt.core.client.JavaScriptObject
      • edu.ucdavis.cstars.client.layers.WMTSLayer.ResourceInfo
  • Enclosing class:
    WMTSLayer

    public static class WMTSLayer.ResourceInfo
extends com.google.gwt.core.client.JavaScriptObject
    An optional resource info object. The default behavior of a WMTSLayer is to execute a WMTS GetCapabilities request, which requires using a proxy page. If resourceInfo is specified a GetCapabilities request is not executed and no proxy page is required.
